text: KLXL may refer to: * Little Falls/Morrison County Airport (ICAO code KLXL) * KLXL (FM), a defunct radio station (91.9 FM) formerly licensed to serve Springfield, Colorado, United States * KTTE, a defunct radio station (90.1 FM) formerly licensed to serve Humboldt, Nebraska, United States, which held the call sign KLXL in 2016
title: KLXL
